summary: PASSING A CONSTRUCTION ZONE ON HIGHWAY (AT SPEED ABOUT 40MPH) , SEVERAL SMALL GRAVELS HIT THE WINDSHIELD AND MADE A FEW CHIPS. SOMETHING LIKE THIS HAPPEND TO MY PREVIOUS CAR TOO, BUT NEVER MADE ANY DAMAGE AT ALL. SO I SUSPECT THE WINDSHIELD ON 2016 SIENNA IS NOT STRONG ENOUGH AND WORRY ABOUT ITS SAFETY.
